        <updateDate>2021-09-01T18:38:06Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Improving Justice Programs through Science Act of 2019</strong></p> <p>This bill reestablishes the Science Advisory Board within the Department of Justice (DOJ).</p> <p>Specifically, it provides statutory authority for the board. Previously, the board was created in 2010 by DOJ and terminated in 2018.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
